{"tid":1823382,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"眾安ZA Bank定期存款門欖1元起 3個月定存達6厘息","createTime":"2020-01-13T15:42:18.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-31T13:47:09.000Z","uid":100322,"like":0,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"1fde2fde3fb806187185b02396e69b9edcbab13d","tid":1823382,"uid":100322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T15:42:18.000Z","msg":"眾安銀行新推出「定期存款加息券」，向合資格客戶提供3個月港元定存息加4厘的優惠，存款額上限為20萬元。以3個月存息2厘計，使用加息券後，存息升至6厘。<br />\n<br />\n作為虛擬銀行，眾安銀行可在互聯網進行不同的銀行服務。以開戶為例，用戶以香港身份證開戶，最快可在5分鐘內完成。用戶在眾安銀行敍造定期存款，起存門欖為1元，而且不設賬戶管理費用。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://bank.za.group/en/waiting-list/home?userShareId=4B6BEC0B215641BDB291D840B494EB32&amp;sourceType=111201\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbank.za.group%2Fen%2Fwaiting-list%2Fhome%3FuserShareId%3D4B6BEC0B215641BDB291D840B494EB32%26sourceType%3D111201&d=x7%2Fg1uS4a%2BT3911x%2BwLoHGg5BW3O7pEdz%2F%2BecHjXtrw%3D&h=609efc7e\" target=\"_blank\">https://bank.za.group/en/waiting-list/home?userShareId=4B6BEC0B215641BDB291D840B494EB32&amp;sourceType=111201</a>"},{"pid":"aada05488feb21b6aee190cd94786455be2d27f5","tid":1823382,"uid":100322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T16:29:08.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"1309eafb6340c831c9a33f1aacafee07b538398a","tid":1823382,"uid":35087,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T16:33:04.000Z","msg":"又送資料"},{"pid":"0b0c0b591b6d481467a9fbf5a388a96443f3042c","tid":1823382,"uid":100322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T17:13:30.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"afd362f32a12647eea5c44dd1d3dcfc1d5136914","tid":1823382,"uid":96871,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T17:18:43.000Z","msg":"咪撚推啦屌 得果百五蚊息 乜撚都比哂人"},{"pid":"fb161d656641996cdfb64e84d265571fa4092c13","tid":1823382,"uid":70019,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T13:47:09.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://bank.za.group/hk/waiting-list/hom